    "body": "@chadyj @hesterbruikman @errorists please let me know what you think on this one.\r\n\r\nThis was a fix delivered in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/5745\r\nThe thing I’m worried is that in terms of usability we did not solve the issue for someone who forgot their password.\r\nSo the only solution for a user (not sure it’s an obvious one) is to re-install the app and recover the account one more time\r\nPerhaps we should recover an account each time the passphrase is valid, no matter the password (so, basically, we would re-set a password for the current user).\r\nThank you.",
